name: Shrimp Running in the Sea
description: Shrimp Running in the Sea. some are extraordinarily colorful and equally animated. Others are drab or transparent and hard to see. Some are active cleaners. Others are scavengers. Some have rather large, sophisticated eyes. Others are blind. Many live in association with the seafloor and only swim occasionally, and some live in association with other animals such as anemones and sponges. Others spend their entire lives swimming in the open sea. Some are smaller than your smallest fingernail.
